[gd_scene load_steps=27 format=3]

; Playable living-city demo: walk among a crowd of citizens running their daily
; routines (commute, work, lunch, gym, bar, home) and bantering in speech
; bubbles. The CityDirector owns the clock; Marker3D nodes in poi_<place> groups
; are the destinations; labelled blocks are the "buildings". Sprint at someone to
; watch them scatter. Self-contained and streaming-safe (groups, no cross paths).

